      "code_id": "6a78f956-f1ef-4fa0-ad8c-296512ee7a7f",
      "code_content": "number = int(input())\n\nk = 1\nfor i in range(1, number+1):\n    pattern = \"\"\n    for j in range(1, i+1):\n        pattern = pattern + (str(k) + \" \")\n        k = k + 1\n\n    print(pattern)\n",
